%20the%20RBI%20from%20commercial%20banks%20on%20the%20money%20it%20lends%20to%20them.%20So%20when%20it%20is%20reduced%2C%20banks%20often%20pass%20on%20the%20benefits%20to%20the%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20Governor%20said%20the%20financial%20year%20begins%20on%20an%20anxious%20note%20for%20the%20global%20economy%20and%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20inflation%20risks%20emerging%20from%20global%20uncertainties.%20This%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20in%20the%20US%20imposed%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20exports%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dent%20on%20global%20growth%20due%20to%20trade%20frictions%20will%20impede%20domestic%20growth.%20Higher%20tariffs%20may%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20net%20exports.%20India%20is%20very%20proactively%20engaging%20with%20the%20US%20administration%20on%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20Governor%20said.%20He%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20quantify%20now%20the%20impact%20global%20developments%20would%20have%20on%20growth.%20But%20he%20said%20the%20central%20bank%20was%20not%20concerned%20about%20being%20able%20to%20manage%20domestic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prospects%20for%20the%20agriculture%20sector%20remain%20bright%20and%20manufacturing%20activity%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20revival%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BServices%20sector%20continues%20to%20show%20resilience.%20Urban%20consumption%20is%20picking%20up%20with%20uptick%20in%20discretionary%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20balance%20sheets%20of%20banks%20and%20corporates%20are%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20Governor%20said%20that%20the%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20had%20noted%20that%20inflation%20is%20currently%20below%20target%20and%20the%20sharp%20fall%20in%20food%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GDP%20growth%20estimate%20for%20this%20fiscal%20has%20been%20cut%20by%2020%20basis%20points%20and%20the%