20International%20Relations%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford%2C%20Professor%20David%20Doyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20been%20outstanding%20in%20her%20two%20terms%20as%20acting%20director%20and%20she%20has%20a%20clear%20and%20compelling%20vision%20for%20the%20next%20stage.%20The%20Reuters%20Institute%20was%20always%20intended%20to%20be%20a%20bridge%20between%20academic%20research%20into%20the%20future%20of%20journalism%20and%20the%20profession%20itself.%20Her%20directorship%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20both%20great%20danger%20and%20extraordinary%20transformation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rusbridger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Institute%20will%20have%20a%20unique%20role%20to%20play%20in%20this%20transformation%20and%20couldn't%20be%20in%20better%20hands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Reuters%20Institute%20receives%20core%20funding%20from%20the%20Thomson%20Reuters%20Foundation.%20Rasmus%20Nielsen%20had%20served%20as%20its%20director%20from%202018%20to%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukherjee%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Bhonoured%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20on%20the%20new%20role%20and%20to%20lead%20an%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20team%20of%20colleagues%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20core%20mission%20is%20to%20explore%20the%20future%20of%20journalism%20worldwide%20through%20debate%2C%20engagement%2C%20and%20research%2C%20and%20I%20am%20looking%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Politics%20and%20International%20Relations%2C%20the%20Thomson%20Reuters%20Foundation%20and%20industry%20partners%20to%20build%20on%20our%20achievements%20and%20mission.%20In%20a%20time%20of%20unpredictability%20and%20shift%20across%20the%20world%2C%20we%20are%2C%20and%20will%20remain%2C%20international%20in%20our%20reach%20and%20impact%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20that%20Mitali%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20named%20Director%20of%20the%20Reuters%20Institute.%20Mukherjee%2C%20who%20has%20been%20Acting%20Director%20since%20October%2C%20was%20selected%20in%20an%20open%20process%20that%20concluded%20in%20late%20March%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOur%20announcement%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAhXFmn1255%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAhXFmn1255%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnDetails%20in%20thread%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbsNyj2uA5r%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbsNyj2uA5r%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Reuters%20Institute%20(%40risj_oxford)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frisj_oxford%2Fstatus%2F1909503997112729844%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%208%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukherjee%20had%20been%20an%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20Reuters%20Institute%20since%20Mr%20Nielsen%20stepped%20down%20last%20year.%20She%20was%20selected%20in%20an%20open%20and%20independent%20process%20that%20concluded%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20TV%2C%20print%20and%20digital%20journalism%2C%20Ms%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20serving%20as%20the%20consulting%20business%20editor%20at%20The%20Wire%20and%20Mint.%20Previously%2C%20she%20has%20worked%20as%20the%20markets%20editor%20at%20CNBC%20TV%2018.%20She%20has%20also%20been%20a%20prime%20time%20anchor%20at%20TV%20Today%20and%20Doordarshan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20a%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20(ORF)%2C%20where%20she%20led%20Gender%20Initiatives%20for%20the%20organisation%20and%20also%20co-founded%20two%20start-ups%20that%20focused%20on%20civil%20society%20and%20financial%20literacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20she%20led%20the%20Reuters%20Institute's%20journalist%20programmes%20since%20September%202022%20and%20represented%20the%20Institute%20in%20conferences%20and%20events%20around%20the%2