E%3Cli%3ERyft%20just%20raised%20%247.3%20million%20in%20Series%20A%20to%20scale%20its%20payment%20infrastructure%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20helps%20financial%20institutions%20handle%20split%20transactions%20for%20booking%20apps%20and%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20got%20an%20exclusive%20look%20at%20the%2016-slide%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20close%20the%20round.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUK%20fintech%20startup%20Ryft%20has%20raised%20%247.3%20million%20in%20Series%20A%20funding%20to%20expand%20its%20payment-splitting%20platform%20into%20new%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20serial%20entrepreneurs%20Sadra%20Hosseini%20and%20Alex%20Mackenzie%2C%20Ryft%20provides%20tools%20for%20marketplaces%2C%20booking%20apps%2C%20and%20food%20delivery%20services%20to%20manage%20multi-party%20payments%20for%20what%20the%20startup%20calls%20%26quot%3Bcommerce%202.0.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommerce%201.0%20was%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20you%20sold%20a%20product%20and%20got%20paid%2C%26quot%3B%20Sadra%20Hosseini%2C%20the%20startup's%20CEO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20in%20commerce%202.0%2C%20%C2%A3100%20might%20need%20to%20be%20split%20between%20a%20driver%2C%20a%20restaurant%2C%20and%20a%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20Ryft%20comes%20from%20%26quot%3Brift%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20in%20a%20split%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Hosseini%20says%20reflects%20the%20startup's%20core%20product.%20The%20platform%20also%20handles%20compliance%20checks%20and%20real-time%20onboarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyft%20makes%20money%20by%20charging%20fees%20on%20transactions%20processed%20through%20its%20infrastructure.%20It%20gives%20acquiring%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20financial%20institutions%20that%20process%20credit%20and%20debit%20card%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20platforms%20the%20ability%20to%20add%20their%20own%20margin%20on%20every%20transaction.%20Ryft%20then%20gets%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20and%20also%20white-labels%20its%20platform%20to%20acquirers%2C%20who%20pay%20for%20access%20and%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERyft%2C%20which%20is%20based%20in%20London%20and%20Manchester%2C%20recently%20partnered%20with%20Clearhaus%2C%20Denmark's%20second-largest%20acquiring%20bank.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Series%20A%20was%20led%20by%20EdenBase%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20GPOS%20Investments%2C%20British%20Business%20Bank%2C%20Pembroke%20VCT%2C%20SidebySide%2C%20and%20Ingenii%20VC.%20Ryft%20also%20brought%20in%20US-based%20Victorum%20and%20executives%20from%20PayPal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHosseini%20said%20the%20startup%20is%20planning%20expansion%20into%20the%20EU%20this%20quarter%20and%20the%20US%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20raise%20this%20to%20survive%20%E2%80%94%20we'd%20already%20broken%20even.%20This%20round%20is%20about%20scaling%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Hosseini%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20means%20international%20growth%2C%20more%20hires%2C%20and%20launching%20omnichannel%20payments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20the%2016-page%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fpitch-deck%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Epitch%20deck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Ryft%20used%20to%20land%20the%20%247.3%20million%2C%20or%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A35.7%20million%2C%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryft%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43639a466d2b74ab277bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERyft%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryft%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f43938a466d2b74ab27868%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%