2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fupcoming-aadhaar-app-to-replace-need-for-physical-card-and-photocopies-125040900264_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Lakh%20Indian%20Students%20Face%20Uncertainty%20As%20US%20Bill%20Plans%20End%20Of%20Work%20Visa%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20proposed%20bill%20in%20the%20United%20States%20Congress%20is%20threatening%20to%20upend%20the%20Optional%20Practical%20Training%20(OPT)%20program%2C%20a%20vital%20work%20authorisation%20initiative%20for%20international%20students.%20This%20move%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20Indian%20student%20community%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20over%20300%2C000%20students%20potentially%20affected%2C%20The%20Economic%20Times%20reported.%20The%20OPT%20program%20allows%20international%20students%2C%20particularly%20those%20in%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20fields%2C%20to%20gain%20practical%20work%20experience%20in%20the%20US%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years%20after%20graduation.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Impact%20on%20Indian%20students%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20students%20are%20the%20largest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20OPT%20program%20according%20to%20the%20Open%20Doors%202024%20report%2C%20with%2097%2C556%20participants%20in%20the%202023-2024%20academic%20year%2C%20a%2041%25%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%20The%20proposed%20bill%20could%20force%20these%20students%20to%20leave%20the%20US%20immediately%20after%20graduation%2C%20disrupting%20their%20career%20prospects%20and%20financial%20stability.%20Many%20students%20rely%20on%20OPT%20to%20repay%20hefty%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECareer%20consequences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill's%20passage%20could%20limit%20job%20opportunities%20for%20Indian%20students%2C%20forcing%20them%20to%20seek%20employment%20in%20countries%20with%20more%20accommodating%20post-study%20work%20policies%2C%20such%20as%20Canada%20or%20European%20nations.%20This%20move%20may%20also%20impact%20the%20US%20job%20market%2C%20particularly%20in%20STEM%20fields%2C%20where%20international%20students%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20addressing%20skill%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERush%20to%20secure%20H-1B%20visas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExisting%20F-1%20and%20M-1%20student%20visa%20holders%20are%20frantically%20applying%20for%20jobs%20that%20can%20transition%20them%20to%20an%20H-1B%20work%20visa%2C%20primarily%20sponsored%20by%20large%20US%20and%20Indian%20technology%20companies.%20However%2C%20securing%20an%20H-1B%20visa%20is%20highly%20competitive%2C%20with%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20visas%20available%20each%20year.%20Students%20are%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20secure%20job%20offers%20that%20would%20enable%20them%20to%20apply%20for%20this%20visa%20before%20potential%20changes%20take%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpert%20insights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoorvi%20Chothani%2C%20founder%20of%20immigration%20law%20firm%20LawQuest%2C%20highlights%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20as%20quoted%20in%20ET's%20report%3A%20%26quot%3BOPT%20allows%20students%20to%20find%20jobs%20in%20the%20US%20for%20one%20year%20after%20they%20graduate%20and%20may%20be%20extended%20for%20another%20two%20years%20provided%20you%20are%20a%20STEM%20graduate%20and%20are%20working%20with%20a%20qualified%20US%20employer.%26quot%3B%20If%20the%20bill%20passes%2C%20students%20may%20lose%20this%20opportunity%20and%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20US%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Indian%20students%20have%20cancelled%20their%20summer%20travel%20plans%2C%20fearing%20they%20may%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20re-enter%20the%20country%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20Prestigious%20institutions%20like%20Cornell%2C%20Columbia%2C%20and%20Yale%20have%20unofficially%20advise