-turns-to-china-as-trumps-tariffs-hit-eu%2Famp_articleshow%2F120113147.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fspains-pm-pedro-sanchez-turns-to-china-as-trumps-tariffs-hit-eu%2Famp_articleshow%2F120113147.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Teens%20Convicted%20Of%20Killing%2080-Year-Old%20Indian-Origin%20Man%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20teenagers%20were%20on%20Tuesday%20found%20guilty%20of%20manslaughter%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20death%20of%2080-year-old%20Bhim%20Sen%20Kohli%2C%20who%20died%20following%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprovoked%26quot%3B%20assault%20while%20out%20walking%20his%20dog%20in%20a%20park%20near%20Leicester%2C%20eastern%20England%2C%20last%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2014-year-old%20boy%20and%20a%2012-year-old%20girl%20who%20filmed%20and%20encouraged%20the%20attack%20were%20both%20convicted%20by%20a%20jury%20following%20a%20hearing%20at%20Leicester%20Crown%20Court.%20Neither%20can%20be%20named%20for%20legal%20reasons%20due%20to%20their%20age%20and%20will%20be%20sentenced%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20tragic%20incident%20shocked%20the%20community%20of%20Leicester%20and%20beyond.%20Mr%20Kohli%20set%20out%20to%20walk%20his%20dog%20in%20his%20local%20park%20as%20he%20did%20every%20day%2C%20but%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20what%20followed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kelly%20Matthews%2C%20Senior%20District%20Crown%20Prosecutor%20at%20the%20Crown%20Prosecution%20Service%20(CPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20shown%20in%20this%20trial%20that%20these%20young%20defendants%20were%20responsible%20for%20Mr%20Kohli's%20death%20-%20in%20an%20unprovoked%20attack%20on%20an%20innocent%20man.%20They%20filmed%20the%20incident%20and%20laughed%20and%20bragged%20about%20it%20afterwards%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20heard%20that%20the%20boy%20was%20the%20principal%20offender%20as%20it%20was%20his%20actions%20that%20resulted%20in%20Kohli's%20death.%20The%20evidence%20of%20the%20girl's%20involvement%20showed%20that%20she%20was%20part%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20in%20encouraging%20it%20and%20filming%20it%2C%20but%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20show%20she%20could%20have%20foreseen%20the%20terrible%20outcome%20of%20the%20boy's%20violent%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20circumstances%20surrounding%20this%20incident%20are%20truly%20tragic%20and%20heartbreaking.%20Bhim%20Kohli%20was%20simply%20doing%20what%20he%20did%20every%20day%2C%20walking%20his%20dog%20in%20the%20park%20that%20was%20just%20yards%20from%20his%20own%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20instead%20of%20being%20able%20to%20enjoy%20an%20evening%20stroll%20with%20Rocky%20on%20a%20warm%20summer's%20day%2C%20he%20was%20confronted%20by%20a%20teenage%20boy%2C%20who%20was%20encouraged%20by%20a%20teenage%20girl%2C%20attacked%20him%20and%20left%20him%20in%20agony%20on%20the%20floor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Detective%20Chief%20Inspector%20Mark%20Sinski%2C%20from%20the%20East%20Midlands%20Special%20Operations%20Unit%20Murder%20Investigation%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSadly%2C%20the%20resultant%20injuries%20were%20fatal%20and%20Mr%20Kohli's%20death%20has%20left%20not%20only%20a%20family%20grieving%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20beloved%20husband%2C%20father%20and%20grandfather%20but%20the%20wider%20community%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20age%20of%20the%20defendants%20in%20the%20case%20has%20added%20to%20the%20devastating%20circumstances%20surrounding%20this%20incident%20and%20complexities%20in%20the%20case.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20enormity%20that%20their%20actions%20resulted%20in%20a%20man%20losing%20his%20life%20and%20the%20consequences%20this%20now%20brings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20convictions%2C%20the%20victim's%20daughter%20Susan%20Kohli%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20family%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20the%20devoted%20life%20partner%20to%20her%20mother%20for%2055%20years%2C%20a%20loving%20dad%2C%20grandad%2C%20brother%20and%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BListening%20to%20the%20enormity%20of%20what%20dad%20was%20subjected%20to%20will%20never%20leave%20us.%20We%20feel%20anger%20and%20disgust%20towards%20the%20teenagers%20who%20took%20dad%20away%20from%20us.%20They%20humiliated%20an%2080-year-old%20man%2C%20assaulted%20him%2C%20filmed%20it%20and%20laughed%20at%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Susan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDad%20did%20not%20deserve%20this%2C%20and%20we%20wouldn't%20wish%20this%20pain%20on%20anyone%20else...%20Losing%20dad%20in%20these%20cruel%2C%20violent%2C%20and%20deeply%20shocking%20circumstances%20feels%20like%20our%20hearts%20have%20been%20pulled%20apart.%20We%20can't%20put%20into%20words%20the%20pain%20we%20feel%20every%20day%2C%20and%20this%20has%20magnified%20during%20the%20trial%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20reference%20to%20some%20of%20the%20trial%20details%2C%20she%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20videos%20showed%20dad%20on%20his%20knees%20being%20hit%20over%20the%20head%20with%20the%20boy's%20slider.%20A%20loud%20horrible%20slapping%20sound%20is%20heard%20when%20the%20boy%20struck%20dad.%20Hearing%20the%20girl%20laugh%20at%20this%20assault%20on%20dad%20is%20utterly%20disgusting.%20This%20sound%20plays%20over%20and%20over%20in%20our%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlso%20captured%20on%20video%20is%20dad's%20attempt%20to%20call%20for%20help%20as%20he%20shouted%20out%20for%20his%20grandson.%20We%20didn't%20hear%20his%20call%20for%20help%20and%20this%20upsets%20us%20deeply.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20evidence%20retrieved%20from%20the%20girl's%20phone%20that%20showed%20harrowing%20footage%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20presented%20to%20the%20jury.%20The%20boy%20admitted%20to%20witnesses%20that%20he%20had%20assaulted%20Kohli%20and%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20a%20social%20worker%2C%20admitting%20what%20he%20had%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%