2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-meta-executive-sarah-wynn-williams-interview-careless-people-book-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESarah%20Wynn-Williams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Facebook's%20former%20head%20of%20global%20public%20policy%2C%20plans%20to%20testify%20to%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20detailing%20allegations%20that%20Meta%20executives%20helped%20China%20advance%20its%20AI%20capabilities%20and%20undermine%20US%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWynn-Williams%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20Facebook%20between%202011%20and%202017%2C%20filed%20a%20whistleblower%20complaint%20in%20March%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20The%20company%2C%20now%20Meta%2C%20said%20she%20was%20fired%20eight%20years%20ago%20for%20poor%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20published%20a%20memoir%20that%20month%2C%20%26quot%3BCareless%20People%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20she%20made%20allegations%20about%20Meta's%20company%20culture%20and%20China%20operations.%20A%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20defamatory%20book%20should%20never%20have%20been%20published.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20book's%20release%2C%20Meta%20won%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-legal-win-bars-former-exec-promoting-book-careless-people-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemergency%20arbitration%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20temporarily%20stopped%20Wynn-Williams%20and%20her%20publisher%20from%20promoting%20the%20memoir%20or%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-prevents-whistleblower-testimony-congress-china-probe-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisparaging%20statements%20against%20her%20former%20employer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20did%20not%20stop%20the%20book%20from%20becoming%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-employee-book-careless-people-sarah-wynn-williams-bestseller-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo.%201%20bestseller%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20gag%20order%20was%20sought%20by%20a%20company%20whose%20CEO%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20champion%20of%20free%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20Wynn-Williams'%20draft%20testimony%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSarah%20Wynn-Williams'%20testimony%20is%20divorced%20from%20reality%20and%20riddled%20with%20false%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20himself%20was%20public%20about%20our%20interest%20in%20offering%20our%20services%20in%20China%20and%20details%20were%20widely%20reported%20beginning%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20this%3A%20we%20do%20not%20operate%20our%20services%20in%20China%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Wynn-Williams%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20draft%20of%20Wynn-Williams'%20opening%20statement%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20obtained%2C%20includes%20allegations%20that%20Meta%20established%20a%20clandestine%20relationship%20with%20China%2C%20providing%20user%20data%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20and%20establishing%20a%20%26quot%3Bphysical%20pipeline%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20the%20administration%20killed%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-and-google-kill-off-hong-kong-undersea-cable-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20project%20from%20Google%20and%20Facebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20have%20established%20an%208%2C000-mile-long%20broadband%20cable%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20Wynn-Williams'%20draft%20opening%20statement%20she%20plans%20to%20give%20before%20a%20Senate%20Judiciary%20subcommittee%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EChairman%20Hawley%2C%20Ranking%20Member%20Durbin%20and%20distinguished%20members%20of%20the%20Committee%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20with%20you%20today.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMy%20name%20is%20Sarah%20Wynn-Williams%2C%20and%20I%20served%20as%20Director%20of%20Global%20Public%20Policy%20at%20Facebook%2C%20now%20Meta%2C%20for%20nearly%20seven%20years%20starting%20in%202011.%20Throughout%20those%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20saw%20Meta%20executives%20repeatedly%20undermine%20US%20national%20security%20and%20betray%20American%20values.%20They%20did%20these%20things%20in%20secret%20to%20win%20favor%20with%20Beijing%20and%20build%20an%20%2418%20billion%20dollar%20business%20in%20China.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20high-stakes%20AI%20arms%20race%20against%20China.%20And%20during%20my%20time%20at%20Meta%2C%20company%20executives%20lied%20about%20what%20they%20were%20doing%20with%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20to%20employees%2C%20shareholders%2C%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20American%20public.%20I%20sit%20before%20this%20Committee%20today%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%20about%20these%20illegal%20and%20dangerous%20activities.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMeta's%20dishonesty%20started%20with%20a%20betrayal%20of%20core%20American%20values.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20pledged%20himself%20a%20free%20speech%20champion.%20Yet%20I%20witnessed%20Meta%20work%20%26quot%3Bhand%20in%20glove%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20to%20construct%20and%20test%20custom-built%20censorship%20tools%20that%20silenced%20and%20censored%20their%20critics.%20When%20Beijing%20demanded%20that%20Facebook%20delete%20the%20account%20of%20a%20prominent%20Chinese%20dissident%20living%20on%20American%20soil%2C%20they%20did%20it.%20And%20then%20lied%20to%20Congress%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20incident%20in%20a%20Senate%20hearing.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20willingness%20to%20censor%20was%20not%20the%20only%20troubling%20thing%20I%20witnessed.%20I%20watched%20as%20executives%20decided%20to%20provide%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20with%20access%20to%20Meta%20user%20data%20%E2%80%94%20including%20that%20of%20Americans.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMeta%20does%20not%20dispute%20these%20facts.%20They%20can't.%20I%20have%20the%20documents.%20As%20recently%20as%20this%20Monday%20they%20claimed%20they%20do%20not%20operate%20services%20in%20China.%20Another%20lie.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EIn%20fact%2C%20they%20began%20offering%20products%20and%20services%20in%20China%20as%20early%20as%202014.%20That%20hasn't%20stopped.%20Their%20own%20SEC%20filings%20from%20last%20year%20show%20that%20China%20is%20now%20Meta's%20second%20biggest%20market.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Meta's%20AI%20model%20%E2%80%94%20Llama%20%E2%80%94%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20Chinese%20advances%20in%20AI%20technologies%20like%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFacebook's%20secret%20mission%20to%20get%20into%20China%20was%20called%20%26quot%3BProject%20Aldrin%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20restricted%20to%20need-to-know%20staff.%20There%20was%20no%20bridge%20too%20far.%20Meta%20built%20a%20physical%20pipeline%20connecting%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China.%20Meta%20executives%20ignored%20warnings%20that%20this%20would%20provide%20backdoor%20access%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20intercept%20the%20personal%20data%20and%20private%20messages%20of%20American%20citizens.%20The%20only%20reason%20China%20does%20not%20currently%20have%20access%20to%20US%20user%20data%20through%20this%20pipeline%20is%20because%20Congress%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMeta%20started%20briefing%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20as%20early%20as%202015.%20These%20briefings%20focused%20on%20critical%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20including%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20explicit%20goal%20being%20to%20help%20China%20outcompete%20American%20companies.%20There's%20a%20straight%20line%20you%20can%20draw%20from%20these%20briefings%20to%20the%20recent%20revelations%20that%20China%20is%20developing%20AI%20models%20for%20military%20use%2C%20relying%20on%20Meta's%20Llama%20model.%20Meta's%20internal%20documents%20describe%20their%20sales%20pitch%20for%20why%20China%20should%20allow%20them%20in%20the%20market%20by%20quote%20%26quot%3Bhelp%5Bing%5D%20China%20increase%20global%20influence%20and%20promote%20the%20China%20Dream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20truth%20about%20what%20has%20gone%20on%20in%20China%20matters.%20I%20filed%20a%20shareholder%20resolution%20asking%20Meta's%20Board%20to%20investigate%20its%20activity%20in%20China.%20And%20I%20filed%20whistleblower%20complaints%20with%20the%20SEC%20and%20the%20DOJ.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20measure%20of%20how%20important%20these%20truths%20are%20is%20directly%20proportional%20to%20the%20ferocity%20of%20Meta's%20efforts%20to%20censor%20and%20intimidate%20me.%20I%20relied%20on%20their%20commitment%20given%20in%202018%20that%20they%20would%20waive%20their%20rights%20to%20pursue%20forced%20arbitration.%20Despite%20that%20public%20commitment%2C%20they%20brought%20a%20case%20against%20me%20for%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars.%20Now%20they%20have%20a%20legal%20gag%20order%20that%20silences%20me%20even%20as%20Meta%20and%20their%20proxies%20spread%20lies%20about%20me.%20This%20order%20is%20so%20expansive%20that%20it%20prohibits%20me%20from%20speaking%20with%20Members%20of%20Congress.%20This%20gag%20order%20was%20sought%20by%20a%20company%20whose%20CEO%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20champion%20of%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EThe%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20the%20truth.%20Meta%20has%20been%20willing%20to%20compromise%20its%20values%2C%20sacrifice%20the%20security%20of%20its%20users%2C%20and%20undermine%20American%20interests%20to%20build%20its%20China%20business.%20It's%20been%20happening%20for%20years%2C%20cover