ies%2C%20new%20job%20titles%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20a%20higher%20salary%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20meet%20more%20of%20my%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20my%20employers%20weren't%20offering%20or%20funding%20any%20professional%20development%20programs%20that%20would%20help%20me%20advance%2C%20though%2C%20I%20took%20my%20development%20into%20my%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20start%20pursuing%20side%20hustles%20that%20would%20help%20me%20improve%20or%20learn%20new%20skills%20and%20also%20get%20paid%20in%20the%20meantime.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20these%20after-work%20gigs%2C%20I%20showed%20my%20boss%20an%20updated%20portfolio%20of%20what%20I%20had%20been%20working%20on%20and%20was%20able%20to%20get%20a%20small%20promotion%20that%20generated%20a%20raise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20get%20paid%20more%20at%20your%20full-time%20job%2C%20consider%20one%20of%20these%20side%20hustles%20that%20can%20help%20you%20nurture%20or%20develop%20new%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22470c6096-8be2-4bf8-8859-61d75ea3be6e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Freelancing%20your%20current%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20side%20hustles%20I%20ever%20started%20was%20easy%20to%20do.%20I%20was%20working%20full-time%20as%20a%20copywriter%20and%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20freelance%20writer%20in%20hopes%20of%20being%20able%20to%20work%20on%20different%20types%20of%20projects%20and%20broaden%20the%20scope%20of%20what%20I%20was%20capable%20of%20working%20on%20as%20a%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20job%2C%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20writing%20scripts%20for%20video%20ads%2C%20but%20through%20freelance%20work%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20work%20on%20blog%20posts%20for%20B2B%20companies%2C%20social%20media%20content%2C%20and%20website%20copy.%20All%20of%20this%20allowed%20me%20to%20improve%20as%20a%20writer%20and%20show%20my%20boss%20a%20portfolio%20of%20updated%20work%2C%20which%20al