ssion%20cubes%20to%20save%20space.%20(Read%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fmonos-carry-on-luggage-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMonos%20luggage%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20about%20why%20Monos%20makes%20our%20list%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-luggage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20luggage%3C%2Fa%3E%20brands.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20tried%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%2C%20I%20was%20hooked.%20While%20they%20are%20expensive%2C%20they%20work%20well%20and%20have%20stayed%20in%20great%20shape%20throughout%20multiple%20trips.%20I%20expect%20them%20to%20last%20for%20years%2C%20and%20they%20have%20already%20outlasted%20several%20cheaper%20packing%20cubes%20I%20bought%20before%20I%20knew%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea243e76-3e26-42cf-9f92-b713c80c130f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Why%20use%20packing%20cubes%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20use%20packing%20cubes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20travel%20frequently.%20I%20usually%20travel%20with%20two%20of%20my%20kids%20and%20like%20to%20travel%20as%20lightly%20as%20possible.%20For%20years%2C%20I%20heard%20others%20rave%20about%20about%20packing%20cubes.%20Nevertheless%2C%20I%20was%20reluctant%20to%20use%20them%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20add%20any%20unnecessary%20weight%20to%20my%20luggage.%20However%2C%20traveling%20with%20suitcases%20that%20are%20a%20disorganized%20mess%20is%20stressful%2C%20especially%20with%20kids%20who%20are%20not%20great%20at%20staying%20organized.%20After%20nearly%20missing%20a%20train%20because%20my%20son%20couldn't%20find%20a%20clean%20shirt%20to%20wear%20in%20his%20messy%20suitcase%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20using%20packing%20cubes%20for%20my%20kids.%20After%20I%20saw%20how%20much%20easier%20they%20made%20it%20for%20my%20kids%20to%20stay%20organized%2C%20I%20began%20using%20them%20for%20myself%2C%20too.%20Now%2C%20I%20can't%20imagine%20traveling%20without%20packing%20cubes%2C%20even%20for%20short%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22307019eb-492f-4ede-bf8f-339ded0308db%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%20and%20specs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20specs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20set%20of%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20on%20the%20floor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f40134c6ad288d147d69b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMonos%20packing%20cubes%20come%20in%20sets%20of%20six%20(shown)%20or%20four.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMonos'%20compression%20cubes%20are%20made%20from%20tear-resistant%20nylon%20twill%20with%20breathable%20mesh%20tops.%20They%20are%20lined%20with%20the%20same%20antimicrobial%20fabric%20Monos%20uses%20in%20its%20suitcases.%20Each%20cube%20has%20two%20anti-catch%20zippers%3A%20one%20to%20close%20the%20packing%20cube%20and%20another%20to%20compress%20the%20cube's%20contents%20if%20desired.%20According%20to%20Monos%2C%20the%20cubes%20can%20compress%20clothing%20up%20to%2060%25.%20I%20generally%20find%20this%20to%20be%20true%20as%20long%20as%20I%20don't%20fill%20the%20cubes%20to%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cubes%20are%20only%20available%20in%20sets%20of%20four%20or%20six.%20The%20set%20of%20four%20is%20designed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-carry-on-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry-on%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20cubes%20in%20this%20set%20are%2013%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%209.8%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B%2C%2013%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%207.1%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B%2C%2010.2%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%208.3%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B%2C%20and%209.8%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.3%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B.%20The%20set%20of%20six%20adds%20one%20larger%20cube%20measuring%2016.9%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%2012.2%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20smaller%20cube%20measuring%207.1%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.3%26quot%3B%20%C3%97%204.5%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20packing%20cubes%20are%20available%20in%20four%20colors%3A%20black%2C%20grey%2C%20tan%2C%20and%20cactus%20green.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22767fb8ae-173c-4b05-9c28-6fc5b38c3438%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20they're%20like%20to%20use%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20they're%20like%20to%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Monos%20packing%20cubes%20in%20a%20carry-on%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f42c513fe8d39283625bc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20packing%20cubes%20feature%20breathable%20mesh%20tops%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20jigsawed%20into%20my%20carry-on%20to%20keep%20things%20compact%20and%20organized.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20immediately%20impressed%20with%20Monos'%20packing%20cubes.%20They%20fit%20a%20ton%2C%20help%20me%20stay%20organized%2C%20and%20have%20kept%20their%20shape%20even%20after%20trips%20to%20a%20dozen%20countries.%20I%20find%20the%20various%20sizes%20useful%20for%20different%20purposes.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20smallest%20packing%20cube%20holds%20enough%20underwear%20and%20socks%20for%20a%20five-day%20trip%2C%20but%20only%20if%20I%20don't%20compress%20the%20contents.%20The%20midsize%20packing%20cubes%20are%20great%20for%20packing%20T-shirts%2C%20sundresses%2C%20and%20shorts.%20I%20can%20easily%20fit%20six%20rolled%20T-shirts%20in%20the%20second-to-smallest%20packing%20cube%20and%20then%20compress%20them%20to%20save%20space.%20I've%20used%20the%20largest%20packing%20cube%20for%20pants%20and%20base%20layers%20when%20traveling%20to%20colder%20climates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20tossed%20the%20packing%20cubes%20in%20my%20day%20pack%20when%20I%20need%20to%20stay%20organized%20while%20I'm%20out%20and%20about.%20On%20a%20trip%20to%20Iceland%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20get%20colder%20when%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20so%20I%20put%20a%20hat%2C%20scarf%2C%20and%20gloves%20in%20the%20small%20packing%20cube%20to%20keep%20them%20together%20while%20I%20was%20out%20exploring.%20They're%20also%20great%20for%20bathing%20suits%3A%20I've%20used%20the%20packing%20cubes%20to%20keep%20my%20swimsuits%20from%20getting%20tossed%20around%20in%20my%20backpack%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20side%20by%20side%20showing%20one%20compressed%20and%20one%20expanded%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f026815d203112923e25ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20shown%20compressed%20(left)%20and%20fully%20expanded%20(right).%20The%20compression%20reduces%20the%20size%20by%20about%2060%25%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20pack%20the%20cubes%20fully%20if%20you're%20planning%20on%20compressing%20them.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20that%20the%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20can%20compress%20my%20clothing.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20the%20packing%20cubes%20compress%20items%20very%20well%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20cubes%20aren't%20filled%20completely.%20I%20find%20that%20I%20can%20fit%20a%20little%20more%20into%20each%20cube%20if%20I%20don't%20compress%20my%20clothing.%20When%20packing%2C%20I%20need%20to%20make%20a%20judgment%20call%20about%20whether%20it%20makes%20more%20sense%20to%20fill%20the%20cube%20or%20put%20less%20in%20but%20compress%20my%20clothing.%20Depending%20on%20the%20trip%20and%20what%20I%20need%20to%20bring%2C%20I%20usually%20do%20a%20mix%3B%20compressing%20the%20clothing%20in%20some%20cubes%2C%20but%20not%20all.%20Accordingly%2C%20I%20recommend%20these%20packing%20cubes%20for%20all%20travelers%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20a%20packing%20cube%20skeptic.%20It's%20nice%20to%20have%20the%20option%20to%20compress%20your%20clothing%2C%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20think%20you%20will%20use%20it%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20have%20three%20sets%20of%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%3A%20one%20for%20myself%20and%20one%20for%20each%20of%20my%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e687b37-1c06-4397-a7f2-9e92b24ba118%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20makes%20them%20stand%20out%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20them%20stand%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20monos%20packing%20cubes%20shown%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f57ce0a466d2b74ab2956f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mesh%20tops%20let%20your%20clothing%20breathe%20and%20allow%20you%20to%20quickly%20glimpse%20what's%20inside.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20dissatisfied%20with%20other%20packing%20cubes%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20Monos'%20packing%20cubes%20really%20stands%20out.%20The%20zippers%20are%20sturdy%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20worry%20about%20them%20breaking%2C%20and%20they%20still%20look%20great%20even%20after%20extensive%20use.%20I%20also%20love%20the%20nice%20variety%20of%20sizes%2C%20and%20the%20mesh%20tops%20that%20help%20me%20see%20what's%20inside%20and%20let%20my%20clothes%20breathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compression%20is%20also%20a%20game%20changer%20and%20a%20relatively%20unique%20attribute%20among%20packing%20cubes.%20I%20love%20that%20the%20packing%20cubes%20not%20only%20keep%20my%20items%20organized%2C%20but%20also%20save%20me%20space%20in%20my%20suitcase%20so%20I%20can%20pack%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218df8d72-50e0-4e16-a519-db0021cadf0e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20packing%20cubes%20are%20lightweight%2C%20but%20they%20feel%20heavier%20than%20some%20others%20I've%20used.%20However%2C%20I'm%20willing%20to%20add%20a%20bit%20of%20extra%20weight%20and%20pay%20a%20little%20more%20to%20have%20packing%20cubes%20that%20work%20well%20and%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20downside%20of%20the%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20is%20that%20they%20are%20only%20available%20in%20sets.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20add%20a%20couple%20of%20midsize%20packing%20cubes%20to%20my%20collection%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20set%20that%20includes%20sizes%20I%20don't%20need%20and%20won't%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20monos%20packing%20cube%20shown%20packed%20with%20clothes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f57c6c3fe8d39283627c0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20use%20the%20compression%20feature%20of%20the%20cubes%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20underfill%20them.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20to%20using%20compression%20packing%20cubes.%20If%20you%20fill%20the%20packing%20cubes%20to%20capacity%2C%20they%20won't%20compress%20and%20the%20zipper%20will%20break.%20I%20found%20this%20out%20the%20hard%20way%20with%20my%20first%20set%20of%20compression%20packing%20cubes%2C%20an%20inexpensive%20set%20from%20Amazon.%20Although%20my%20Monos%20packing%20cubes%20are%20sturdier%2C%20I%20find%20that%20if%20I%20fill%20them%20when%20they%20are%20fully%20expanded%20they%20won't%20compress%20without%20using%20a%20lot%20of%20force.%20I'm%20not%20willing%20to%20risk%20breaking%20a%20zipper%20on%20such%20an%20expensive%20set%2C%2