C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20government%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Suryodaya%20Yojana%2C%20the%20shift%20to%20solar%20power%20has%20become%20more%20accessible.%20The%20scheme%20offers%20subsidies%20covering%20up%20to%2060%25%20of%20installation%20costs%20and%20provides%20loan%20support%20for%20the%20remaining%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstalling%20solar%20power%20is%20surprisingly%20simple.%20Modern%20photovoltaic%20(PV)%20panels%20can%20be%20fitted%20on%20rooftops%20that%20receive%20adequate%20sunlight%20and%20require%20minimal%20maintenance.%20A%20typical%20solar%20panel%20has%20a%20lifespan%20of%2025%20to%2030%20years%2C%20making%20it%20a%20long-term%20investment.%20Additionally%2C%20net%20metering%20policies%20let%20you%20sell%20excess%20electricity%20back%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20earning%20credits%20on%20your%20power%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20cost%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20numbers.%20The%20cost%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352016%2Fhow-to-harvest-solar-energy-panels-in-apartments-homes-rentals-guide-to-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstalling%20a%20solar%20panel%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2045%2C000%20to%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20kilowatt%20(kW)%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%C2%A0%20location%2C%20and%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20small%20household%20using%20around%20200%20to%20300%20units%20of%20electricity%20per%20month%20may%20require%20a%202%20kW%20system%2C%20co