%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20her%20dream%20faced%20immediate%20opposition.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20my%20dad%2C%20sports%20can%20never%20be%20a%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Shraddha%20had%20made%20up%20her%20mind%20to%20turn%20her%20passion%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259633%2Flovlina-borgohain-tokyo-olympics-medal-india-proud-village-assam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20into%20a%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20decided%20on%20the%20niche%20but%20knew%20that%20martial%20arts%20was%20where%20she%20belonged.%20Social%20media%20helped%20her%20make%20the%20final%20decision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shraddha%20performing%20her%20creative%20forms%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T160018.291-1744021852-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20foundational%20training%20in%20taekwondo%2C%20Shraddha%20learned%20new%20tricks%20and%20forms%20via%20social%20media.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20scrolling%20through%20YouTube%20and%20found%20videos%20on%20tricking%20(a%20training%20method%20that%20combines%20kicks%2C%20flips%2C%20and%20gymnastics).%20I%20was%20intrigued%20by%20the%20different%20movements%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%2014%20at%20the%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20natural%20step%20was%20to%20learn%20the%20art.%20But%20Shraddha%20did%20not%20have%20a%20coach%20to%20train%20her%2C%20nor%20could%20she%20afford%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20teenager%20and%20did%20not%20have%20the%20family%20support%20to%20ask%20for%20financial%20help.%20It%20forced%20me%20to%20find%20other%20ways%20to%20learn%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20go%20for%20%3Cem%3EKanjak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(young%20girls%20are%20worshipped%20as%20representations%20of%20the%20Goddess)%20during%20Navratri%2C%20earn%20Rs%20100%2C%20and%20save%20it%20for%20registrations%20and%20tournaments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESocial%20media%20to%20the%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShraddha%20quickly%20realised%20that%20pocket%20money%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20her%20long-term%20goals.%20She%20needed%20substantial%20funds%20for%20tournament%20registrations%20and%20personal%20expenses.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202020%2C%20I%20started%20to%20post%20videos%20of%20my%20training%20on%20social%20media%2C%20not%20just%20to%20showcase%20my%20skills%20but%20to%20build%20a%20platform%20for%20people%20who%20do%20not%20have%20the%20financial%20backing%20to%20learn%20tricking%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20popular%20belief%2C%20kickboxing%20is%20more%20than%20just%20fighting%20with%20and%20defeating%20opponents%3B%20it%20serves%20as%20an%20umbrella%20term%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20martial%20arts%20events%20that%20also%20include%20creative%20forms.%20And%20Shraddha%E2%80%99s%20passion%20shines%20brightest%20in%20the%20sport%E2%80%99s%20musical%20forms%20that%20blend%20powerful%20kicks%20and%20flips%20with%20martial%20arts%20and%20gymnastics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20to%20do%20martial%20arts%20with%20the%20beat%20of%20music%20%E2%80%94%20we%20are%20not%20dancing%2C%20though%2C%20but%20we%20are%20fighting%20with%20shadows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shraddha%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDHTbfndy6sw%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDHTbfndy6sw%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdi