ia.com%2F32273%2Fmohammad-iftekhar-khan-in-kickboxing-nationals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Kickboxing%20Championship%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20secured%20two%20gold%20medals.%20This%20momentum%20carried%20her%20into%202024%2C%20a%20year%20packed%20with%20international%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20demanding%20schedule%2C%20with%20the%20WAKO%20World%20Cup%20before%20the%20Asian%20Kickboxing%20Championship%202024%2C%20she%20had%20virtually%20no%20time%20for%20specific%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20performances%20I%20was%20giving%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20Asian%20Championships%20were%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20With%20two%20major%20events%20on%20the%20horizon%20and%20only%20three%20months%20to%20prepare%2C%20she%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20relentless%20training%2C%20sacrificing%20even%20her%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20her%20routine%2C%20Shradhha%20shares%20that%20she%20starts%20her%20day%20with%20a%20five-hour%20training%20session%20from%205%20am%20to%2010%20am.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%2011%20am%20to%2012%20pm%2C%20I%20try%20to%20study%20during%20exams.%20In%20the%20afternoon%2C%20I%20have%20footwork%20or%20technical%20sessions%20from%201%20pm%20to%203%20pm.%20Post-lunch%2C%20I%20have%20one%20more%20session%20either%20in%20the%20gym%20or%20sparring%20(fighting)%20with%20my%20teammates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shraddha%20with%20her%20achievements%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi