.%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20of%20females%20do%20not%20experience%20chest%20pain.%20Instead%2C%20they%20may%20have%20hand%20pain%2C%20jaw%20pain%2C%20excessive%20sweating%2C%20giddiness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20or%20breathlessness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20prevent%20this%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreventing%20heart%20disease%20begins%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffirst-aid-for-heart-attack-part-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20routine%20health%20monitoring%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Dr%20Rao%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20one%20should%20check%20blood%20pressure%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year.%20The%20target%20should%20be%20a%20systolic%20pressure%20below%20130%20and%20a%20diastolic%20pressure%20below%2080.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20keeping%20cholesterol%20levels%20in%20check%20is%20crucial.%20%E2%80%9CA%20total%20cholesterol%20level%20should%20be%20below%20200%2C%20and%20LDL%20should%20always%20be%20less%20than%20100%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20healthy%20sugar%20levels%20also%20plays%20a%20significant%20role%3A%20An%20LDL%20below%20100%2C%20a%20three-month%20average%20sugar%20level%20below%205.7%2C%20and%20a%20fasting%20blood%20sugar%20level%20below%20100%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rao%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T152523.508-1744019734.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu