e%20the%20men%20of%20the%20Sundarbans.%20They%20wade%20through%20marshy%2C%20murky%20waters%20teeming%20with%20crocodiles%2C%20snakes%2C%20and%20pneumatophores%20(the%20spiky%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20mangrove%20forests%2C%20spanning%20an%20area%20of%2010%2C277%20sq%20km%20%E2%80%94%20to%20fetch%20a%20coveted%20prize%2C%20which%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20world%20is%20honey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sticky%20elixir%20is%20their%20main%20source%20of%20livelihood%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20global%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20while%20one%20eye%20is%20on%20the%20water%2C%20the%20other%20constantly%20scans%20the%20swamp%20bank.%20In%20the%20delta%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20green%20eyes%20and%20a%20flash%20of%20yellow%20and%20black%20equates%20to%20a%20death%20sentence.%20And%20the%20locals%20have%20taken%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20forewarn%20visitors%3B%20Mumbai%20native%20Neeti%20Goel%20(48)%20was%20no%20exception.%20In%202022%2C%20during%20her%20first%20trip%20to%20the%20archipelago%2C%20she%20was%20stunned%20to%20hear%20that%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352436%2Fmangrove-plantation-sundarbans-afforestation-conservation-south-parganas-west-bengal-cyclone-blind-activist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20tiger%20widow%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20(women%20whose%20husbands%20were%20killed%20by%20tigers)%20stood%20at%20over%203%2C000.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201